Plain sentence:
---------------
    Satan has a vast advantage in such cases to ply them with various temptations, which he is not wont to neglect : in such
    a case, persons very much need a guide to lead them to an understanding of what we are taught in the word of God
    concerning the nature of grace, and to help them to apply it to themselves.

